id: 2653
name: Buying Strength
power: 2
text: |
  A player CAN Buy Strength by paying a fee of 1 Votive. A person's
  Voting Strength on a referendum on an ordinary proposal is 1
  greater for every time e Bought Strength during that decision's
  voting period.
